Mixed chemicals are used in the The Dig Site to create the chemical compound. It is made by combining nitroglycerin with ammonium nitrate, granting 2 Herblore experience. The chemicals can then be combined with ground charcoal, granting 2.5 Herblore experience, to make step 2 of the compound. Finally, it can be combined with an arcenia root to make the chemical compound, granting 3 Herblore experience. Due to the nitroglycerin, dropping the mixed chemicals will cause an explosion that destroy the item and deals a significant amount of damage to the player. The chemicals deal 45 damage after step 1, or 55 damage after the addition of ground charcoal in step 2.
